    "description": "《Devil's Drizzle》是一款迷人的2D像素艺术平台游戏，讲述了一个勇敢的孩子追寻他的可靠雨伞的故事，穿越黑暗、多雨的景观，同时遭遇苏美尔恶魔。<br><br>游戏引入了一种独特的游戏机制，玩家在完全黑暗、多雨的环境中应对挑战，仅靠他们可以控制的闪电来照明。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/6f2fbc351cfa3cfcd611842a630d63a3.poster.avif?t=1739063669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/6f2fbc351cfa3cfcd611842a630d63a3.webm?t=1739063669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/6f2fbc351cfa3cfcd611842a630d63a3.mp4?t=1739063669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一款可爱又黑暗的游戏，设定在一个充满奇幻世界的背景下，其故事充满激动人心和充满挑战的时刻。具有多样的机制，让人联想起经典的平台游戏：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>双跳<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>场景照明<br></li><li>敌人<br></li><li>可收集物品<br></li><li>多种结局</li></ul><br>还有各种风格的关卡，如：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>经典平台<br></li><li>'载具'关卡<br></li><li>'飞行'关卡<br></li><li>'自由落体'关卡<br></li><li>'追逐'关卡<br></li><li>Boss战斗</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/613f5d02bf59a04da043dfaed58f74dd.poster.avif?t=1739063669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/613f5d02bf59a04da043dfaed58f74dd.webm?t=1739063669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071140/extras/613f5d02bf59a04da043dfaed58f74dd.mp4?t=1739063669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
